title: EQ Brain Performance
description:
EQ reinvents the way athletes, patients, and medical staff assess anxiety, lack of sleep, concussions and more.
• Clinically-derived tests
• Use on yourself, your children, or your teams
• FDA Listed as a Class II 510(k)-exempt
• CE Marking
• Fun for the test-taker

== Aids in the assessment of anxiety, lack of sleep, concussion and more ==
EQ contains seven neurological tests, all clinically-tested and helpful in the assessment of neurological impairments/conditions such as anxiety, lack of sleep, concussion and more. In the event of a worrisome event, a comparison test can be run, and the results should be shared with a qualified practitioner.

== On-the-spot analytics and monitor progress over time ==
Immediately analyze test results on your mobile device. Easily monitor and track progress over time to establish a healthy range of results, making it easier to identify outliers and potential issues.

== FDA listed, CE Marking, clinically evaluated ==
EQ is FDA listed as a Class II 510(k)-exempt medical device and has obtained CE Marking and is registered in the EU to comply with the European Medical Device Directive. All of our tests have been clinically evaluated. 
 
== Backed by the brightest minds in medicine and sport ==
Highmark Interactive's Medical Advisory Board and Professional Advisory Board represent the foremost thought leaders on neurology, traumatic brain injury, concussion, and how they impact athletes. Read more at https://www.highmark.tech/#aboutus.

== Fun to play, easy to monitor ==
EQ uses engaging games to test the brain and rewards users for playing with unlocks like fun fans to cheer them on. Not only will they enjoy doing the tests, but they're also incentivized to try harder!

== Integrates with Apple's Health app ==
If you collect your sleep and step data on the Health app, you can share them with EQ: Ensure your Apple Health app is tracking steps and sleep then initiate sharing from EQ’s Account or Stats page and you will see your daily values on EQ’s stats screen. 

Subscription Details:
Get a 7-day free trial - no payment required, just download and start testing! After your free trial, you can choose to subscribe on a monthly or annual basis. You can also choose an individual or family plan that allows for up to 5 users per account. If you change your mind at any point, cancellation is easy through your iTunes settings.
• The remainder of your trial period will be forfeited when purchasing a subscription.
• When you confirm your purchase, payment will be charged through your iTunes account.
• Your subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.
• Don't want to auto-renew? Manage your account and renewal settings in your user Account Settings.
• You can use your subscription on any device registered with your Apple ID.
• Cancel your subscription anytime through your Account Settings, without a cancellation fee.
• If you need help or have questions, get in touch at contact@highmark.tech
• Results obtained during your trial will be carried into your paid subscription

Privacy Policy: https://www.highmark.tech/privacy-policy/

Terms of Use: https://www.highmark.tech/terms-and-conditions/

title: BLACKROLL® Fascia Stretching, Flexibility Training
description:
In this APP you will find versatile and highly-efficient exercises for self-massage, recovery and functional training using the BLACKROLL® products.

Get a BLACKROLL® roll- and workout for each body part, BLACKROLL® product or training level, all in one APP.

Download the APP on your phone and roll into a fitter life!


YOUR TEAM BLACKROLL®


---

OUR GOALS

Your physical health is what matters most to us. That is why we produce tools and create exercises that directly aim to improve this.


BLACKROLL® offers people of all ages and sports levels the possibility to improve their flexibility, balance, and strength by doing simple exercises and applying self massage. They are the optimal addition to classical treatment methods, such as physiotherapy, massage, Rolfing or osteotherapy.

We encourage you to try out the exercises with the BLACKROLL® products and experience how this will positively influence your fitness, performance and general well-being.

Let’s get rolling!

BENEFITS
- Improves flexibility, mobility and performance of the muscles.
- Prevents muscle pain and typical injuries like muscle damage, occurring from overuse or repetitive movement.
- Targeted recovery of the muscles and improvement of blood circulation.
- Improves poor posture through balance work.
BLACKROLL® allows for multifunctional use: workout and roll-out.
- Actively enhances your fitness, performance and wellbeing, and avoids pain, such as typical (sport-related) injuries.

WHAT ARE FASCIAE?

The musculature functions because its being held together by an essential but often overlooked tissue: the fasciae. This connective tissue surrounds and permeates every muscle, bone, nerve and organ; simply said it’s the stuff that keeps us together.


Fascia is comparable to a three-dimensional full body suit, which forms a network of supporting structures. Research proves that the fasciae have a great influence on our posture, quality of movement, pain perception, and muscles. These are the elements of our body on which self myofascial release, or self massage, has an influence to prevent muscle pain and improve the recovery ability of muscles.

title: How to Treat a Concussion
description:
When a blow to the head shakes the brain within the space between the brain and the skull, the resulting shaking is known as concussion.A concussion is the most common type of head injury. A concussion can result from a car crash, a sports injury, a fall, or a violent shake to the head or upper body.

While most concussions are a temporary disturbance that don't leave lasting damage, it can lead to associated serious problems if not treated promptly and effectively.

comments: Good info, but arranged more like a basic website than an app. Also the information is more focussed on acutely after a concussion. It feels like the app was produced as a school project. What would be helpful is more clear terminology (less academic and/or medical) and maybe a tool to rate symptoms over several days and then see the score of the symptoms to see if certain areas are improving or worsening.

comments: This app is great until it's not. Even though I have all notifications turned off I still get notified about everything. And I mean EVERYTHING! On Sundays suring football season it's one notification after another every two to three minutes all afternoon. If you ever need customer support forget it. There is none within the app. It's literally nonexistent. So if you have a problem, you're on your own. Good luck!

I have turned off all notifications. And I'm still getting notifications on everything, every 30 minutes. I just want to follow my team, at my leisure. If I can't get this to stop, I'll just delete and block the app. I do... like the fact that games are free to watch on the app, makes it convenient on the go, and don't have to wait till I find a tv.

I bought the gamepass option to listen to live games. That does work; HOWEVER, you have to keep the phone display ON the whole time and can't do other apps while listening to the game. Every other major streaming audio service allows the app to run in the background, but not NFL. Very annoying for $100 per year.

nfl gamepass is the biggest scam going.....I can't believe a huge corporation like the nfl would blatantly try to scam lifelong fans.....i tried it....it was so so at best.....most of the time it didn't work.....so I figured I wouldn't get it again.....simply wasn't worth the money......so what does nfl scammers do.. ..they billed me automatically for the next season even though I never asked to renew it!!! then refused to give me my money back when I told them the app hasn't worked all season!!

"Clickbait Notifications" I like this app, it's clean and clear and has decent reporting. But my word the notifications are infuriating and the reasons I've deleted the app. "This player from the NFC East has been traded. Open to find out who". "A two time Pro bowl player has been benched". I haven't got time for that. I manage my phone through my notifications, so if your giving my notifications that tell me nothing, I'll go find another app that sends me meaningful information.

title: Physiotherapy
description:
"Physiotherapists help people affected by injury, illness or disability through movement and exercise, manual therapy, education and advice. 
They maintain health for people of all ages, helping patients to manage pain and prevent disease.
The profession helps to encourage development and facilitate recovery, enabling people to stay in work while helping them /content/what-physiotherapto remain independent for as long as possible.

What physiotherapists do
Read the evidence
Our Physiotherapy Works briefings demonstrate the effectiveness of physiotherapy in treating a wide range of conditions
Physiotherapy is a science-based profession and takes a ‘whole person’ approach to health and wellbeing, which includes the patient’s general lifestyle.
At the core is the patient’s involvement in their own care, through education, awareness, empowerment and participation in their treatment.

You can benefit from physiotherapy at any time in your life. Physiotherapy helps with back pain or sudden injury, managing long-term medical condition such as asthma, and in preparing for childbirth or a sporting event.
Why physiotherapy?

Physiotherapy is a degree-based healthcare profession. Physios use their knowledge and skills to improve a range of conditions associated with different systems of the body, such as:

Neurological (stroke, multiple sclerosis, Parkinson's)
Neuromusculoskeletal (back pain, whiplash associated disorder, sports injuries, arthritis)
Cardiovascular (chronic heart disease, rehabilitation after heart attack)
Respiratory (asthma, chronic obstructive pulmonary disease, cystic fibrosis).
Physiotherapists work in a variety of specialisms in health and social care. Additionally, some physiotherapists are involved in education, research and service management.
"

You can benefit from physiotherapy at any time in your life. Physiotherapy helps with back pain or sudden injury, managing long-term medical condition such as asthma, and in preparing for childbirth or a sporting event.
Why physiotherapy?

Physiotherapy is a degree-based healthcare profession. Physios use their knowledge and skills to improve a range of conditions associated with different systems of the body, such as:

Neurological (stroke, multiple sclerosis, Parkinson's)
Neuromusculoskeletal (back pain, whiplash associated disorder, sports injuries, arthritis)
Cardiovascular (chronic heart disease, rehabilitation after heart attack)
Respiratory (asthma, chronic obstructive pulmonary disease, cystic fibrosis).
Physiotherapists work in a variety of specialisms in health and social care. Additionally, some physiotherapists are involved in education, research and service management.
"
summary: Physiotherapy education

title: Virtual Hospital Family Doctor Surgeon Emergency
description:
The 3d virtual doctor is a new innovative and a real family doctor game with amazing gameplay environment and controls you would love to play just like other medical games. In this game you play the role of a doctor that conduct the treatment of patients with various diseases. 
The virtual hospital doctor games is based on a real life of a doctor in which you just have to work as the virtual doctor to operate the patients by identifying there disease and start the treatment. As the patient come to the emergency care centers on rescue ambulance the hospital duty is to check the previous medial record of the patient and forward those to the suitable doctor for better treatment and then your roles start as a doctor. You are provided with various tool to find the either the symptoms of the disease of patient on daily basis or as emergency doctor to deal with patients injured during some accidents occurs in city rescue by the ambulance such as 911 operators. This ambulance rescue the patient and point hospital that is the nearest one and take it into the emergency.

This doctor simulator game contains the different skill levels of the doctor. The doctor skill level increase as he perform the patient treatment successfully. First you with low skill level only treat the patient on regular basis and as the level increases you need to deal with the patients with more critical health conditions in emergency rooms and also have to perform various operations like heart surgeries, liver transplant and critical wound treatments. As the level increases you are awarded with various rewards and bonuses.
 
Gameplay 

First the patient come to the doctor hospital the emergency hospital staff categorize the patient as for the regular checkup or emergency if patient wants regular checkup he has to wait for his turn. You as a doctor examine the patient and on the basis of the symptoms identify the disease the patient has and start the disease treatment by suggesting them either medicines or further tests.

In emergency situations you need to quickly respond try to heal the wounds in a given time and perform operations by following the time limits beware if any step goes wrong or times out the patient may die which can affect the game points or may decrease in level . AS the level of your game increase different category of operations and tools will be unlocked.

Features

•	Realistic environment with amazing graphics and easy controls 
•	Endless missions and tons of patients are waiting for you
•	Various operation and treatment tools
•	Play as a specialized doctor and save life’s
•	Intuitive easy to uses user interface

title: IBJI Access
description:
IBJI Sports Access is here when an injury occurs. Quickly request a complimentary injury screen or find details to visit one of our OrthoAccess walk-in clinics.

Complimentary Injury Screens

Complimentary injury screenings are evaluations performed by a Licensed Physical Therapist (PT) or Certified Athletic Trainer (ATC) in our physical therapy clinic as a means to help our patients determine what is the best treatment solution for non-emergency conditions. An IBJI clinician will explain the extent of the injury and educate the patient on an appropriate treatment protocol.

OrthoAccess

OrthoAccess is a walk-in clinic designed to quickly and affordably treat simple fractures, sprains, strains, work and sports injuries and more. Staffed by certified IBJI orthopedic specialists and supported by advanced diagnostic technology. Specific IBJI OrthoAccess clinics are even open on weekends!

Stop by an OrthoAccess Clinic when…

* Your Little Leaguer crashes into home and hurts his elbow
* You slip and fall at work
* Your weekend warrior tears a hamstring
* Your ankle twists on the way out the door
* You fall off the bike and something breaks

OrthoAccess Advantages

* Be seen without an appointment
* Be seen same day and in significantly less time compared to an ER visit
* Get great care from IBJI orthopedic specialists
* Have onsite access to advanced diagnostic technology and services
* Receive treatment in an environment that’s calm, family-friendly and professional
* Save up to 80% compared to the cost of an ER visit

title: GOWOD
description:
Do you practice functional fitness? 
Download GOWOD for free to test and improve your mobility in a completely personalized way!
Unleash all your athletic potential, reduce your risk of injury and accelerate your recovery in your functional fitness practice. 

GOWOD offers you to test your mobility and your personal flexibility and allows you to improve it thanks to effective mobilization protocols adapted to your weak points and your functional fitness practice. GOWOD lets you know how to mobilize before or after your workouts, whether you are in the box or at home. 
Whether it's to improve your performance, speed up your recovery, improve your well-being or reduce your risk of injury, GOWOD adapts to each context to guide you easily in your practice of mobilization and stretching. GOWOD is the perfect tool to accompany you in your practice of functional fitness.  

Features:
Free body mobility test to discover your strengths and weaknesses. 
More than a hundred videos of high quality mobilization exercises available for free and perfectly adapted to the practice of functional fitness.
All mobilization videos classified by body zones, type of exercises or equipment, accompanied by a description of the performance points to be respected for an optimal execution of the exercises.  


GOWOD PREMIUM: PERSONALIZED MOBILITY.

 By opting for GOWOD Premium, you push the limits of your progression, improve your safety in the face of training injuries, and gain access to a total personalization of your practice of mobilization exercises and stretching. 
Test GOWOD Premium FREE for 14 days!
Renewable mobility test every month to observe your progress. 
Unlimited use of personalized mobilization protocols Pre-WOD, post-WOD and Daily.

GOWOD Premium is the practical, simple and effective solution that you would have liked to have since you started practicing functional fitness. 
Download the application for free, and start unlocking your potential now.

APPLICATION AND SUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION
Downloading and using GOWOD is completely free of charge. The features of GOWOD Premium are accessible thanks to a monthly subscription with no obligation of duration and can be subscribed directly from the application. By subscribing to GOWOD Premium you pay monthly the fixed price for your country, which is displayed in the application before the validation of your subscription. The subscription is renewed automatically every month, except in the case of cancellation at least 24 hours before the current subscription expires. Your account will be debited within 24 hours before the current subscription expires. The current subscription cannot be cancelled under any circumstances, but the automatic renewal can be terminated at any time from your account settings.

If you have any further questions about the GOWOD application, please do not hesitate to contact us at contact@gowod.eu

comments: Like the wide variety of selections. There are a lot of different excercises to choose from and the timer is a great way to keep track. Mobility tests are interesting but it's the same thing; nice if it switched it up every few months. Lately I have been experiencing a weird bug for 22min are actually 15min stretches. The library is the best feature because it shows EVERYTHING!

Fantastic app, really great concept of being able to measure initial mobility and track progress. The daily routine it gives you is programmed to the most weak aspect from your first test. The instructions for each movement are pretty good, I'd probably want a little more detail on some of them. Scaling sometimes just says 'reduce range' which isn't always helpful but the stimulus tab is brilliant for informing what you should be feeling during the movement/stretch.

It was great as a mobility test, but trying to sign up for premium is a hassle, I've tried to subscribe, but it keeps saying invalid card, even though I have a legitimate bank account as well money to pay for it.

So glad I use this app. I've become so much more mobile and the use of the monthly testing keeps me wanting to improve further. Love this app and highly recommend. GET IT NOW! You're seriously missing out on massive improvements

I love this app so much. The Daily Protocol being tailored to your needs is great and I can see the progress im making, physically in the movement itself, and with visually with the percentage rating on the app. I like that the mobility ratings are accumulated in a graph. I think the Pre and Post Wod element is great too as you enter the movements that you're using in your workout and it generates a tailored sequence for you. I can see my squats getting deeper and my overhead ability improving

title: ESPN
description:
Watch thousands of live events and shows from the ESPN networks plus get scores, on-demand news, highlights, and expert analysis. Subscribe to the ESPN+ streaming service for live sports, exclusive originals, premium articles, fantasy tools, and more.

Watch on ESPN:
• NFL (Monday Night Football) • NBA • MLB • College Sports (football, basketball, baseball, softball, and more) • Golf (The Masters) • Soccer (UEFA Euro and MLS) • Tennis (Wimbledon, US Open, Australian Open) • eSports • ESPN Shows (SportsCenter, PTI, First Take, Sportsnation, NBA: The Jump, and more) •

ESPN+ Subscribers:
Stream exclusive live sports and ESPN+ Originals without cable--all in HD.

Sign up for ESPN+ and get access to the streaming service that delivers live sports from the best leagues in the world plus premium articles and fantasy tools. Get live events from the UFC, MLS, NHL, international soccer, college sports, and more. Enjoy the complete 30 for 30 library and exclusive ESPN+ Original shows from the biggest names in sports including Peyton Manning, Dana White, Kevin Durant, Alex Morgan, and more all inside the ESPN app.

Highlights and scores from what you care about. From news about your favorite sports or team playing right now, the home tab has you covered. Fast access to scores for your favorite teams and leagues and the top games of the day in the scores tab. Also, subscribe to your favorite ESPN Podcasts or listen live to ESPN Radio.

ESPN, ESPN2, ESPN3, ESPNU, SECN, and more are all available to stream live in the ESPN App. Access to live video is determined by your TV provider and package and, in some instances, your Internet service provider.

Due to contractual limitations with certain content, especially play-by-play broadcasts, there are times when the schedule that's on-air won't match the schedule that's online. If you have specific schedule questions, please contact the station directly by visiting their website.

comments: Plus: selecting teams/leagues that I like to follow so their info is readily available, notifications, and game times. Minus: getting notifications and info on all the stuff I don't like at all (looking at you UFC). Wish I could select what things I don't want to see. Minus x 2: very often when I tap to open an article, it goes to a completely different article. This happens probably 20% of the time I'm on the app.

If you want to read an article it will work...sometimes, or it will just give you an article that it decides you want instead. Want to stream something, sure, just get comfy as it buffers every 20 seconds or so whether it's your mobile device or you PC so a college game takes 5 hours, not that you can seen it properly because of pixelated buffering. This doesn't happen in any of my other streaming services, just this. Worldwide leader in sports, dumpster fire of digital media.

Too many bugs. Many articles do not load completely and some just load the first few lines and then nothing but vertical lines. It's a mess! The loading issue was fixed, but now the article links take you to the wrong story. Streaming is ok, but it does drop out too much. Update: loading issues fixed but the links are always messed up. Clicking on a story takes you to a completely different story.

I have the espn, disney, hulu bundle. Espn app works 10% of the time. I'm constantly trying to log into my provider to watch live TV. Tonight I tried to watch a college football game on espn3. It keeps telling me that Im not authorized to watch the stream, which is false, or it can't authentic my provider. This is more than annoying. I pay a subscription for your app and it doesn't even work right have of the time.

Update: October 9. Still buffering for pretty much everything. I just download stuff over night and watch offline. Recently, sound is not synchronized with video. Really hard to believe how bad this app is. Original post: Even with measured 200-300mb download speed, the app buffers repeatedly. I don't know if it is a server side issue or the app itself. However, I can only rate my app experience as average, at best. And, compared to services like Netflix, it is far below average.

Working on flexibility is important for lots of reasons, and having optimal joint range of motion can lower your risk of injury and increases your quality of life. Achieving the splits means, that someone has impressive flexibility in their hips, glutes and hamstrings. However, before you go from zero to splits, know that it’s going to take some time to get there.
Follow our 30 days splits training! ;)

Best 30 days Guide To Doing The Splits

Intuitive video guide

title: Hoop League Tactics
description:
Hoop League Tactics is a fresh new take on the sports management simulation genre. Take control of your basketball team and lead them to victory in turn-based tactical action. Manage your players between games by upgrading their skills and scouting for the next prospect to join your squad. Whether you'd rather control every action or watch from the sidelines, how you decide to play the game is entirely up to you!

Features:

- Turn based tactical gameplay featuring three pointers, dunks, blocks, steals, and more.

- Create and fully customize multiple basketball leagues by changing team names, uniforms, and even court colors. Edit any player's name, appearance, and ratings.

- Choose a league and take your own basketball team through an in-depth Season Mode. 

- Draft players, negotiate contracts, and improve your team after every game with player progression and skill trees.

- Manage your players fatigue and keep them fresh with load management to prevent injuries. Players will eventually retire after they've played too many seasons.

- Play, watch, or simulate your own games and other team's games around the league.

- Increase fan support and team chemistry to gain more income to purchase team upgrades and attract players at a lower cost.

- Full stat tracking for every player and team across multiple categories.

- Earn individual accomplishments for your players from multiple end of season awards.

- Qualify for the post season tournament and lead your team to the championship.

- Continue playing for multiple seasons and win as many championships as possible!

comments: Overall its a good game, but it needs more features. I want to see a career mode, make the game longer and more like nba games with 12 minute quarters and please make it to where each team can have 15 players instead of 10. And spread out the scoring, it seems like when the rotation is in place only the starters score, and during the season, make it to where you can turn fatigue off or lesson fatigue because the load management is sad. And btw, we should have individual stats instead of stars.

I LOVE THIS GAME! HOWEVER I have issues with the fact that players with "Excellent" durability can fatigue faster than players with "Bad" durability. The usage amount of the player should not matter if they have good durability. Also players with 10 shooting and shooting abilities should not go 0/5 from 3 shooting 60%+ shots. Its aggravating

Too simplistic/repetitive. Once you find something that works, it works every time. Defense never changes. In my first championship in my first season, I shot over 91% on Pro difficulty. Too easy. I also received a trade offer after the last game of the season. But since the season was over, I couldn't accept it. And contracts negotiations are terrible. If the player doesn't accept your 1st offer, you lose them forever. Did the developers bother to play their game? Good concept, poorly executed.

It was a nostalgic and enjoyable game. I love the old school vibes it gives off. I love the season aspect to it too but would love to see a "Myplayer" game mode where you create and design your personal player and see it fail or succeed through the season.

Honestly a real fun addicting game but the simulating feels broken, I genuinely have one of the best teams and was 11-0 playing and thought I would sim to get to the playoffs faster and I've lost 7 straight? The game is honestly so fun but this is so irritating

title: RotoGrinders - DFS Strategy, Lineups, and Alerts
description:
Winner of the “Best fantasy content app” award (FSGA), the RotoGrinders DFS app provides all the content and tools you need to reach the top of the leaderboard.
Alerts, lineups, tools, optimizers, news, analysis, and more, the RotoGrinders daily fantasy sports app is your one-stop shop for all your DFS needs, including uploading lineups to Draftkings and Fanduel in seconds.

If you’ve ever felt lost building DFS lineups without a computer in front of you, we’ve taken all the main components to building lineups like the experts and turned it mobile – the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app. Whether you just want to build one optimal lineup or enter 150 into a GPP, we’ve got you covered, and the best part is you can upload the lineups you create directly to DraftKings and FanDuel in seconds. 

Once you’ve entered lineups, stay up to the minute on all pertinent DFS breaking news, late scratches, lineup changes and weather information with the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app! It’s absolutely a must-have for anyone trying to turn a profit playing daily fantasy sports. 

Our team of dedicated daily fantasy analysts monitor a number of sources and alert you of anything you need to know to build the best possible DFS lineups each night. Not only do we post starting lineups and injury news faster than anyone in the industry, but we also tie that into analysis to help users apply that information in the most useful way. In past years you’d have to stay at a computer constantly to stay up-to-date, but our ability to send push alerts to mobile phones allows our users to manage their DFS lineups and entries on the go. 

Make no mistake – the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app does more than optimize lineups and send push notifications as soon as news is announced. To help you turn these alerts into action, all notifications contain priority and analysis from our RotoGrinders team of experts. This late-breaking news can greatly affect lineup construction on any given day, especially in daily fantasy NBA and MLB. 

The RotoGrinders DFS app allows you to:

- Optimize lineups with the help of our Expert Filter Picks – Core, Cash Plays, GPP Plays, Salary Savers and Conviction Plays.

- Build up to 150 different lineups using advanced settings and upload them directly to DraftKings or FanDuel through the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app.

- Manage entries and adjust to late-breaking news.

- Receive push notifications when high priority news breaks (late scratches, injury updates, game cancellations, etc).

- View our DFS Alerts feed in the app, including alerts and applicable DFS analysis of all priority levels, sortable by sport.

- Be alerted when daily lineups are released and access them (as well as that team's DFS salaries) with a single click.

- Manage notifications to only receive alerts for the sports or sites you want.

- Play Grinders Live shows in audio-only format as well as making the podcasts available after the fact.

Sports supported:
- NFL
- NBA
- MLB
- NHL
- PGA
- College Football
- College basketball
- NASCAR
- MMA
- ESPORTS
    - LOL (League of Legends)

descriptionHTML:
Winner of the “Best fantasy content app” award (FSGA), the RotoGrinders DFS app provides all the content and tools you need to reach the top of the leaderboard.
Alerts, lineups, tools, optimizers, news, analysis, and more, the RotoGrinders daily fantasy sports app is your one-stop shop for all your DFS needs, including uploading lineups to Draftkings and Fanduel in seconds.

If you’ve ever felt lost building DFS lineups without a computer in front of you, we’ve taken all the main components to building lineups like the experts and turned it mobile – the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app. Whether you just want to build one optimal lineup or enter 150 into a GPP, we’ve got you covered, and the best part is you can upload the lineups you create directly to DraftKings and FanDuel in seconds.

Once you’ve entered lineups, stay up to the minute on all pertinent DFS breaking news, late scratches, lineup changes and weather information with the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app! It’s absolutely a must-have for anyone trying to turn a profit playing daily fantasy sports.

Our team of dedicated daily fantasy analysts monitor a number of sources and alert you of anything you need to know to build the best possible DFS lineups each night. Not only do we post starting lineups and injury news faster than anyone in the industry, but we also tie that into analysis to help users apply that information in the most useful way. In past years you’d have to stay at a computer constantly to stay up-to-date, but our ability to send push alerts to mobile phones allows our users to manage their DFS lineups and entries on the go.

Make no mistake – the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app does more than optimize lineups and send push notifications as soon as news is announced. To help you turn these alerts into action, all notifications contain priority and analysis from our RotoGrinders team of experts. This late-breaking news can greatly affect lineup construction on any given day, especially in daily fantasy NBA and MLB.

The RotoGrinders DFS app allows you to:

- Optimize lineups with the help of our Expert Filter Picks – Core, Cash Plays, GPP Plays, Salary Savers and Conviction Plays.

- Build up to 150 different lineups using advanced settings and upload them directly to DraftKings or FanDuel through the RotoGrinders Daily Fantasy app.

- Manage entries and adjust to late-breaking news.

- Receive push notifications when high priority news breaks (late scratches, injury updates, game cancellations, etc).

- View our DFS Alerts feed in the app, including alerts and applicable DFS analysis of all priority levels, sortable by sport.

- Be alerted when daily lineups are released and access them (as well as that team's DFS salaries) with a single click.

- Manage notifications to only receive alerts for the sports or sites you want.

- Play Grinders Live shows in audio-only format as well as making the podcasts available after the fact.

Sports supported:
- NFL
- NBA
- MLB
- NHL
- PGA
- College Football
- College basketball
- NASCAR
- MMA
- ESPORTS
- LOL (League of Legends)
- CS:GO
- Rocket League

Along with being a Daily Fantasy Sports Lineup Optimizer, the RotoGrinders DFS app also provides push alerts and lineups for a variety of sports. This is your go to lineup app for MLB, NFL, NBA, League of Legends and more.

This is your one-stop lineups and news app for your daily fantasy sports games. Download now and have everything you need to build and upload your DFS lineups on the go.

title: Emergencies in Sports Medicine
description:
This Oxford University Press app-book,Emergencies in Sports Medicine, is developed by MedHand Mobile Libraries. Improve your performance with relevant, valid material which is accessed quickly and with minimal effort in the palm of your hand using Medhands patented technology.

Functions include: 

•	A powerful search 
•	Bookmarks, History and Highlighting  
•	Complete set of medical calculators; Body Mass Index, Peak Expiratory Flows, Dehydration Correction Calculator and more 
•	Notes and picture notes

Aboutthistitle

•	Covers all aspects of sports medicine, from event planning, and communication to common sports-related emergency situations
•	Key chapters are devoted to the different parts of the body that are commonly affected in sporting events
•	Ideal for doctors working at sporting events
•	Written by an expert team of authors and editors, including the doctor for Chelsea Football Club Academy

Part of the bestselling Emergencies in ... series, Emergencies in Sports Medicine is the ideal book for any doctor to keep in their kitbag or locker. This essential easy-to-use guide provides guidance on the immediate care for patients with sporting injuries. The portable format, practical approach and easy-reference layout mean that information can be rapidly found in emergency situations.

Covering every type of sporting emergency from head injuries to altitude sickness, this crucial volume appeals to a wide audience, from the doctor involved directly in sports medicine to the doctor who occasionally watches their children play sport and is concerned that they will occasionally be called upon to give medical advice. It will also appeal to allied health professionals involved in any aspect of sport. The book will also help organizers to plan in advance for larger sporting events.


Authors: Edited by Julian Redhead and Jonathan Gordon

________________________________________ 

MedHand Mobile Libraries offers a SUBSCRIPTION FREE application without edition upgrade. Offering most trusted and well recognized medical guidelines provided by excellent publishers like Oxford University Press, McGraw-Hill, Pharmaceutical Press, Wiley, Elsevier and more.

comments: This is the best baseball game on android. Unless someone can suggest a better game, I'm sticking with this. It is not hard to adjust to the controls, and you don't even need to spend real money to build your team, so just be patient and keep getting the free 10 gems. Also, learn to work the count, make the opposing pitcher wear himself out. My current team in Master II is a beast, and unbeaten towards the end of the season! If you need a great baseball game on your device, MAKEIT THIS ONE!!

This game is 5 star for lots of reasons. It's got great graphics, great gameplay, and great competition levels. The only reason why I am writing this review though, is to give you some ideas for future updates. The biggest thing that I would love to see in the game is Wild pitches. It would be an amazing add the the game. Also, more celebrating after stuff. Like, when you hit a walk-off or win a league. If all of these things were added, I would have put 6 stars

OK Look. This game is fabulous. Its amazingly fun. Its really great! Try it out!!! But the only problem is that its really hard to get gems to customize your stadium, uniform, or logo. I have still had the same default uniform, stadium, and logo for 1 month now and i play the game every day... Otherwise, its good.

The game was good but I'm not sure if it's getting to higher levels or not but there are way too many line drives caught especially by the 1st & 3rd basemen. It seems like 75% of the outs are line drives and not enough lines drives that are his unless they are doubles. The game isn't enjoyable anymore unfortunately.

I like this game because it's Baseball. But I hate how your players get tired every 2-3 games and you have to give them energy drinks. That happens constantly. Also, I'm ok with losing here and there but there should be no reason that I lost 11 games in a row even though everyone on my team was non injured (I just noticed that today) and everyone is in perfect condition and is not tired. That's absolutely garbage.

title: Deep Tissue Massage Treatment Guide
description:
Everything You Need to Know About Deep Tissue Massage!

Is a Deep Tissue Massage What Your Muscles Need?

Deep tissue massage is a massage technique that’s mainly used to treat musculoskeletal issues, such as strains and sports injuries. 
It involves applying sustained pressure using slow, deep strokes to target the inner layers of your muscles and connective tissues. 

Step by step treatment routines Guide for the most commonly encountered neuromuscular conditions are clearly outlined using detailed descriptions and illustrations side by side. 

This helps to break up scar tissue that forms following an injury and reduce tension in muscle and tissue.
It may also promote faster healing by increasing blood flow and reducing inflammation.

comments: There is far too much luck and not enough strategy in this game. One can use the same level balls, lined up on the same dot, pointed in the same direction, on the same alley, use the same swing; and one week you get strikes or 9s. Next week, tons of splits. The flower pin arrangement is a very good example. The game does not reward figuring out strategy. It also does not provide enough opportunities to upgrade balls. It also does a poor job of pairing u against opponents with same ball level.

Fun! All free for me so far. Update: I still really enjoy playing this game. The graphics are incredible and the ways the balls, pins and alleys interact seems to be 100% true to the laws of physics. Sometimes I'll get startled by the ball or pins shooting back in my face or I'll burst out in a laugh when something unexpected happens. This is still one of my go-to games even when I'm losing.

Your game is the best bowling, most realistic and I used to bowl pro. But it freezes up constantly. Its really frustrating when your bowling for 6,000. I've probably lost 15,000 easy. Please fix the freezing! The lower right side still freezes my stick. I like the changes, however, the one u call Rabbit, 2configuration of 5 pins. These games r to challenge yourself.the only way to get a strike is by accident. Please change the one, no fun.

This app is filled with a bunch of bots. The whole system is rigged. What a disappointment. The balls don't get any better. How I know it's rigged and you aren't playing against live players is try and forfeit in the last frame beforeit even begins. Miraculously it shows the other persons score over those 3 frames when there wasn't even enough time to bowl those 3 frames. Rigged!!!

title: EA SPORTS UFC®
description:
Step into the Octagon® with EA SPORTS™ UFC® for mobile! Collect your favorite UFC fighters, throw down in competitive combat, and earn in-game rewards by playing live events tied to the real world of the UFC. 

This app offers in-app purchases. You may disable in-app purchasing using your device settings.

FEEL THE FIGHT
EA SPORTS UFC brings the intensity of MMA to your fingertips like never before. HD-quality visuals, intuitive touch controls, and action-packed gameplay create a unique combat experience for novice and veteran fight fans alike.

TRAIN YOUR ULTIMATE FIGHTER
Choose from over 70 fighters in four divisions and begin your journey to the top. From a Cain Velasquez takedown to Georges St-Pierre’s Superman punch, each athlete boasts a unique set of special moves. Win bouts, unlock new opponents, earn coins, and level up abilities – all while building your UFC legacy. Battle through your career and invest in training to watch your abilities skyrocket.

PLAY LIVE EVENTS, EARN EXCLUSIVE REWARDS
Play some of UFC’s biggest real-world bouts through in-game Live Events. Play fight cards for upcoming UFC events and earn exclusive in-game rewards. The more you play, the more rewards you earn! Rise to the top of the leaderboard and watch your payoff grow.

FIGHT YOUR WAY TO GLORY
Climb the ranks and hone your striking, wrestling, and submission skills along the way. With no lives or limits to how much you can play, there’s always another fight just around the corner. See how you stack up against your division’s best and earn in-game rewards for dominating UFC icons in grueling Main Event matchups. Your battle for UFC glory starts now.

Enter the Octagon and feel the fight!

Important Consumer Information. This app: Requires a persistent Internet connection (network fees may apply). Requires acceptance of EA’s Privacy & Cookie Policy and User Agreement.
. Includes in-game advertising. Contains direct links to the Internet and social networking sites intended for an audience over 13.

User Agreement: terms.ea.com

EA may retire online features after 30 days’ notice posted on http://www.ea.com/1/service-updates.

comments: It's a wonderful time killing game, but once you get passed stage 45 the characters you are fighting will double in there health, power etc; when you and your opponent are on even power on all earlier stages. Then stage 45 comes and your opponent is on a power level of 2000 and you are still on power level 800, what are you supposed to do?...and even worse it stays at this unfair disadvantage (basically it needs a ranking system) (Otherwise your only choice is to rage or switch characters)

The game itself is not so bad. Nothing too much to do but a decent time killer. The thing that bothers me is that ea so blatantly attempted this to be a cash grab for them. In-game transactions are not optional, they become more of a necessity. After a few rounds the opponents start coming so overpowerd that it literally becomes impossible to climb to their level without using real money. I am at level 219, my health is 9000 and the opponent i am fighting has a health of 65k. Really ea?

Sad. More EA sadness. Can't move yourself around with a left toggle, it pushes you in automatically. You just spam punch in hopes it lands, randomly tapping an icon on the left side of the screen where you should be able to move, for special attacks...ground and pound is quickest to accumulate abilities on takedowns/grapples. Really its not a good experience at all, for a fighting style about "control." If i wanted to play a tap "boxing" game, id play that AND be able to control my character.

Overall, this game is pretty alright. But it gets mundane pretty early on. Graphics aren't that great either. An obvious money grabber from EA. Watch UFC and play the latest games on console, this one just isn't it. Hoping for another developer to come along and revolutionize this franchise, but until then, stay on consoles :)

Could be better if the computer followed the same set of rules as the player, player can NEVER punch the computer fighter out of a special move but the computer can ALWAYS simply punch the player to completely stop any special move, computer can use body hook to stop take down, player cannot, also it is physically impossible to knock someone out by kicking them in the shin

- 27 different patients with radically different ways to save
- Easy, fun touch gestures that mimic real surgery activities

Notes: For level 3, you need to recharge the patient first and then give him several injections.

title: Stretching exercise. Flexibility training for body
description:
Stretching exercise & Flexibility training– is just the right application for any person, who cares about his health.
Nowadays people often have low activity levels and sedentary lifestyle, so to do flexibility stretches pre and post-workout is very important for anyone. All stretching exercises for beginners were selected to develop the elasticity of the body and do not require any additional equipment.

Stretches for flexibility
The daily stretch workout is suitable for all groups of people. There are 60 different routines to do flexibility training for beginners, and all of them have detailed video and text instructions. Just follow the instructions of the virtual instructor

Everyday morning warm-up
What could be better than a charge of vivacity and energy in the morning? Just do a workout and see how your health gets better and better every morning. In addition, the morning flexible workout has a great influence on mood throughout the day and overall vitality. Flexibility training for beginners, for gymnastics, for men and women has 3 different programs and over 50 different workouts during which you can do the full-body training.

Warm-up
Before performing any physical exertion, for example, when running or when visiting the gym and pool, all muscles must be prepared and heated. The warm-up will allow you to do stretches to improve leg flexibility and to prepare the muscles and avoid their overtraining, possible injury and damage. 

Muscle tension and pain relief
Muscular tension - constantly increased muscle tone when it is impossible to fully relax them. The specially designed training system will get rid of muscle cramps and blocks. What makes this happen? In carrying out the sports activity, there is an increase in the local blood flow, especially in the muscles and ligaments, due to which the local metabolism and metabolic processes are enhanced. So, if you have flexible muscles - everything will be ok. Do the upper and lower body, leg stretch, shoulder stretching exercises for beginners.

Application functionality:
✓ 60 different stretching exercises for beginners for the full body of different levels of complexity and for all muscle groups;
✓ Each stretch routine contains detailed audio, text instructions and videos of their implementation;
✓ 3 training programs are provided and prepared for stretch workout for every day, you can also create your own workouts, set the level of difficulty and length, also every program has different stretch plan and different difficulty – Basic program is the best choice for the beginners, 7 minute or 10 minute stretch exercises – is for everyday stretching workout;
✓ We've created a special motivation system that will keep track of your results and motivate to achieve more and more;
✓ You can create your own programs for leg flexibility stretches for beginners, for runners;
✓ Notifications system - Now, you will never forget to do stretch fitness;
✓ Detailed statistics – make a 30-day challenge and track your results and your progress.

We use a special system to test our elasticity. To do this, we offer to regularly measure our indicators:
1) The distance from the fingertips to the floor when tilted forward - characterizes the general condition of the spine and its health. Just do flexible stretches for men and women, even for runners and the results will come!
2) The distance from the center of the palm to the level of the knee when tilting sideways from a standing position - here is the condition and elasticity of the back and waist when tilting.
3) The distance to the floor from the position when the person sits on the splits - if the muscles of the legs are clamped and their elasticity is missing, then this is a very difficult task.

⭐ The main task of this app is not only to do body flexibility training for beginners, men & women, for gymnastics, - but to create a stable habit of regular stretch exercises in the context of life.

comments: This is a good app with 3 complimentary workout programs in the free version. I am doing the basic. I like it so thought I'd get the premium as it promises 50 extra workouts. I paid for premium and there is still only 3 workouts. I can't see any different between free and paid. Did they mean up to 50 extra exercises? Disappointed.

The measurements aren't realistic for everyone. My split measurement was 17 my husband's was 25. The highest you have is 11. It also wouldn't allow me to put 0 in for the side measurement even though it's an option. I would love to see a stretching app for specific sports too.

Simple doable postures that may be perfected over iterations. Even though I'm 53, this app helped me to a more flexible physique.
Nice exercising app. It's really helping me especially during this lockdown when i gained weight and I needed to go back to being flexible

comments: Great game, love the controls and the graphics. However, I don't like the way the matchmaking is working. I always get stronger opponents (generally way more agility or serve than me so I can barely hit the ball) and I'm not willing to put money in this game considering that it must be like that anyway. I would love a PVE mode like tournaments.

It is a fun game but trophies thing is bad, like it locks higher tours if you lose trophies in lower tours. pro pass and purchases are expensive. Nevertheless, there is a need to spend money. Also, the game stucks sometimes in the middle of a match. In addition, sometimes the game does not load on my phone, it reaches to 74% then stucks. If the above are improved, it will be the best tennis game i played.. Improve the this please. Too much frustrating. Thanks

This game totally sucks. At first I loved to play but I noticed constantly that it seems the game cheats so your opponent can win. So balls or superspeed for the other players even though I have great stats. This is a total scam game to get you to pay money. I'm pretty sure it's matching you with boys or the creators so you automatically gonna lose. I'm deleting this game because it is a total lie and scam. This game has made me want to stop trusting game sites. Your all in it for the money.

Really fun. The controls are very easy to learn, and hard to msster. The stats and gear help, but a good player can beat someone with much better gear. So its not P2W. It takes time to open loot bags that you get for winning. And you can watch ads to take 15 mins off. Not bad at all. And no surprise ads either. You only watch if you want to. Would reccomend. If you like pvp, try it. If you like tennis, try it. If you like to waste time. Play it. Only cons are entry fees and upgrade costs.

This game can be very fun. Unfortunately it glitches constantly. Opponent will appear to miss a ball. Then suddenly it is past you. Or you swing, and suddenly it is past you. Or better yet, you never even see a hit or serve, and suddenly your opponent has a point. Sometimes, an opponent who's has nowhere near the skill or agility is all over the court, and hitting zingers. It is really fun when there are no glitches, but extremely frustrating it isn't working right.

title: Heart's Medicine - Doctor's Oath - Hospital Drama
description:
Become a doctor in a romantic medical drama with aspiring intern Allison Heart!

GameHouse and Blue Giraffe proudly present the latest GameHouse Original Story, starring your favorite doctor, Allison Heart! 
Heart's Medicine - Doctor's Oath is an intense medical drama tied to a casual game that’ll move you to tears. The game has a gripping and unique storyline, original singer/songwriter music, highly detailed artwork and animation, cool addictive gameplay and an insane amount of heart. If you enjoy games that focus on great storytelling, this game is for you!

❤️ Experience the life of a doctor as you rush to find a cure for an unknown disease!
❤️ Your search for a cure will take you through six exciting new hospital wards, from the Clinic to the Morgue.
❤️ Play the full game with no extra charges, thanks to our free-to-play model. 
❤️  More levels to play than ever before! Enjoy 240 levels at launch, with more to come!
❤️ So many extras! Unlock new story scenes, level up your character to earn helpful bonuses, and purchase the upgrades YOU want to buy
❤️  Party with Oliver and his guinea pig friends, Punky and Olive.
❤️ Master new mini-games like a true doctor, all in medical style.
❤️ Additional levels will be added in the future, giving you even MORE of the game you love!


Follow Allison as she begins her last rotations as an intern at Queensburrow Bridge Hospital, on her path to graduating as a fully-fledged doctor! Unfortunately, things never go smoothly for Allison, and this is no exception. Dr. Ermey, the lead physician during her clinic rotation, seems to have it in for her, and threatens to fail her. Allison ends up watching her chances of becoming a doctor shrink by the minute, desperately searching for a solution, but unable to find one.
However, everything gets put on hold when a patient with a mysterious disease is admitted to the hospital. Several doctors end up becoming infected themselves, including Connor, Sophia… and Dr. Ermey. When the CDC quarantines Queensburrow, it’s a race against time for Allison and the other doctors to find a cure before more deaths occur. 
Your assistance will be invaluable to Allison as she tries to beat the clock and find a cure in time! Experience love, intense action, realistic drama, crazy funny moments and the beauty of celebrating life in Heart’s Medicine – Doctor’s Oath.

Follow Allison on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/heartsmedicinegame/

Follow GameHouse on Facebook:: https://www.facebook.com/GameHouseOriginalStories/

*Download the GameHouse Original Stories app and enjoy other amazing games like Delicious, Dr. Cares and Fabulous:* https://goo.gl/SXb8sa

comments: I absolutely love this game it gives you back story, intrigue, and a real interest in the characters. I absolutely love it!!! I love story line it makes things that much more interesting and this game has everything to keep you hooked, it definitely has me. I just wish there was a way to get energy either from friends or from watching ads more because I hate waiting until my energy fills up again maybe they can work that in some how but honestly I have no issues with the game it's GREAT 👍👍👍👍

Love this game series I am subscriber. I don't mind the in app purchases I've made a few. My problem is the special events, I have the same problem with them all. Currently with the Halloween I have gotten to chest number 8 and am no longer getting credit for the skulls I've earned. So I can never finish an event. I stopped playing for awhile because of this issue and the fact that I can't get support in the game to work either. I haven't gotten credit for the skulls in the last 3 levels

I have been playing this game for a long time now and it's wonderful with the storyline and the game play it's been improved drastically. The only thing I'm complaining about is that it has a few bugs. When I just played I had a level with Ryan and a mobile clinic with tray decay and limited tray space. As soon as I pressed play, it cleared the entire level for me without me even playing with a score of zero and then I was stuck on the menu. It also crashes and I lost energy.

I have played all the Heart's Medicine games, and even purchased the monthly subscription to play them. This game however is completely different.. I hate the fact that there are now in app purchases and an energy system. I loved this game franchise BECAUSE it wasn't pay to play. Why are you shoving countless "special offers" in my face? I want to actually play and experience the story.. but now I see that money has become more of a priority. I cannot describe how disappointed I am.

Such a great game but the thing that I don't like about it, is how the couples kiss in the game. But its still a great game and I love how there is different items that you can purchase from the shop to make your docters office more better with the items! And I also love how there is speed so if you need help because your slow you can purchase speed with only 10 💎 and I use the speed alot for help when I start playing the game. ♡

title: Real Boxing 2
description:
"The boxing game we deserve." 8/10 – Gamezebo
"A big, brash boxing game that's surprising tactical at heart." 8/10 – Pocket Gamer
"Stunning graphics powered by Unreal Engine 4." — App Advice
"Not just a button masher." – Slide to Play

FIGHT FOR GLORY
Enter the ring and get into epic punch-out matches in the ultimate free fighting game for mobile. Face dangerous opponents in the ring and score a knockout! Explore the world of pro boxing and make your way to the top – You can become the boxing champion, the best of all time! Welcome to the best of fun fighting games and get ready to punch hard, boxer. 

JOIN AN ENDLESS MMO FIGHTING EXPERIENCE
Challenge an elite of boxing games champions and players from around the world of punching games: fight night or day in single and multiplayer gameplay modes across hundreds of exciting events, story mode, and smackdown tournaments.

ENGAGE IN FAST PACED ON-THE-RING ACTION
Become the ultimate boxer. ąMaster jabs, hooks, uppercuts & combine them with devastating Special Punches and Focus abilities. As in the top free fighting games, you can create the ultimate combos to KO your opponent in a fierce smackdown. Nothing is more satisfying in a boxing game or a mma game than an early knockout!

BATTLE AGAINST UNIQUE BOSSES
Here’s a new spin on punching games: take on a unique type of challenging opponent, each one available to challenge for a limited time. Clown? Check. Santa? Yeah he’s there. Golem of the rocky variety? You bet. Defeat them all to claim their epic gear!

CHOOSE YOUR STYLE OF BOXING GAME
Before the true punch-out begins, develop your boxer’s stats and unlock new abilities to level up your fighting game. Equip powerful boosts to create your own unique fighting playstyle. It’s a bit like wrestling or mma : it’s best to enter the punch-out and serve a smackdown in style. The true punching games are about to begin and a knockout is in the air!

UNLOCK HUNDREDS OF POWERFUL ITEMS
On the rocky path to becoming a boxing champion you gain access to a huge number of unique, upgradable and customizable gear, enhancing fighting stats and abilities of your boxer one step, one punch, one round at a time.

CREATE THE ULTIMATE BOXING FIGHTER
Use a robust set of options to create your own boxer – from body mass and muscle sculpture, to details as small as nose shape, fun fighting games like this let you create your own fighter.

CONNECT WITH FRIENDS
Feeling like becoming a champion and playing fight games with friends? Invite them over and punch out them in real-time PVP action to find out who’s the best boxer right here and now. Fight for the quickest knockout and best scores across a variety of leaderboards. 

PLAY EXCITING MINI-GAMES
Fun fighting games included: train your fighter in exciting mini-games and try your luck in the Daily Lottery for a chance to win awesome rewards.

FEEL THE POWER OF UNREAL ENGINE 4
It’s the fight night time: witness jaw-dropping graphics fully utilizing the power of Unreal Engine 4 technology to create the most dynamic knockout experience and the best of visually stunning MMO free fighting games.

Real Boxing 2 is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. A network connection is also required.

Contact us anytime at support@vividgames.com

Follow Real Boxing 2 on Facebook: www.facebook.com/realboxing.

comments: This game is focused on making its players worse whenever a player gets knocked out he cant get up he needs to spend gems coins or watch a ad but whenever a bot gets knocked out he gets super fast this, games last no more than 45 seconds and the graphics could better i think if they used there money from their ads and chagnged the game up it could be better but from now on i wont reccomond this game to friends

It seems it doesn't even know simple addition dropping it down from a 2 to a one. Visually pleasing however the fights are really underwhelming. This could be a good game if you try to make it one however it seems that you just dont want to try.

title: Tom Leg Surgery Doctor Game
description:
Tom was walking next to the hospital when a terrible accident happend. Tom had a broken leg, this is an emergency! Let's call a doctor. The hospital is close, so we can go there now to do a surgery. Tom, the patient from this accident, had so much pain that he agreed and they went straight to the hospital. His leg injury needs to be fixed, a surgery will be needed said the doctor in this emergency.

Tom's leg was hurt, so the surgical patient operation began immediately. Too bad that the doctor had an emergency to go himself, so he asked you to help Tom. Will you fix Tom's leg injury in the hospital? You only have to do the surgery with for example a knife, forceps, bone clamp and a retractor. This time in hospital you only have to do it on a virtual leg of the patient, because this is an emergency.

You will need a couple of things to fix the leg injury of Tom in the hospital. The doctor said that all the leg surgery equipments will be on the emergency table. So here we go.

We see the table in the surgery room and there are things like these on it to help the patient:
- Forceps
- Retractor
- Surgical Knife
- Bone Clamp
- Forceps with cotton plug
- Bovie
- Bone Plate
- Bone Screw
- Hand Drill
- Surgical Suture
- Screw Driver

Tom will thank you forever if you will fix his virtual leg injury. The hospital will thank you also, including the doctor. His emergency went well, but he thinks that your job was even greater. If you do these kind of surgery in the hospital in the future, you could be a great doctor. Thanks for helping Tom, his leg is healthy now.

In this doctor game you can be the doctor! Help Tom, he broke his leg!

We hope you will enjoy this leg injury surgery doctor game and we hope you give us the love by likening our Facebook page or follow us on twitter. So we can keep you up to date on our fashion games, girl games, hair salon games and more!

★Twitter - https://twitter.com/ladiesdressup

title: Triathlon Manager 2020 - Free games
description:
Do you like extreme sports? In ClickAthlon Manager you can manage professional triathlon teams, participate in incredible multiplayer races with teams from all over the world.

Prepare yourself for an experience like you've never had before in sports games, choose the best strategies, plan the team's training sessions, thinking about giving your best on the slopes.

Experience the challenge of sports management, it is a game of athletic racing, bike racing and the toughest water challenges like swimming in the open sea or swimming pool competitions.

Compete against thousands of triathlon teams around the world, experience the life of a triathlete as an extreme athlete, prepare, train, improve training facilities, get the best equipment, compete against more than 10,000 athletes, improve your speed and endurance skills.
 Multiplayer online game: 
You will compete against players from all over the world for being the best in every event and competition. Will you be able to beat everyone and be number 1?

Train all kinds of disciplines, from Swimming, Cycling or Athletics Series to Weight Series, Crossfit, Spinning, etc.

You will also have all kinds of swimming tests to compete against your rivals and improve your own brands until you reach the gold medal. You have evidence of swimming in the pool, in open water.

You can also run track races, you can run marathon. Not only that get on the bike and try track cycling, cross bike, sprint triathlon, Olympic triathlon, long distance triathlons, duathlon in all its distances, aquatlon, etc.

ClickAthlon is an extreme sports simulator which has generated a community that is growing every day and where there is a great atmosphere around the triathlon, you can get to know each other in the various chat rooms, as well as meet rivals and great friends.

 Directs the sports career of an Olympic athlete: 
ClickAthlon has all kinds of national and international rankings to promote and statistics in which to progress, Under-18, Under-23, WTT, rankings by categories or by tests in addition to point competitions each season.

 Be a true manager 
ClickAthlon also allows you to create your own club or participate in an existing one, where you will have to fight side by side with your teammates to be the best club every season, for this you will need to work with the other members of your club, plan strategies and think about how Invest to improve the benefits of your club.

In the free olympics game you can act as manager or coach to take the career of a youth to the highest divisions.

In ClickAthlon you will have a series of achievements and tasks to perform every day and every season, but you can also set your goals yourself, win the general classification, a category, beat the record of your country in 100 free meters or simply improve your brand in 10,000 smooth meters.

You can choose the design of your avatar with a large number of accessories of all kinds, giving it a more professional, or totally crazy look, now you can also equip your avatar with the best equipment, bicycles, shoes, swimsuits, tritrajes, gym equipment , everything you can imagine to help you get as far as possible.

In extreme sports, diet or supplementation will help you deal with fatigue, achieve better results or heal injuries,
In addition, improving your trainers, your facilities or your equipment will make your progress faster.

title: ready – fit for #teamarmee
description:
Mit der ready App der Schweizer Armee kannst du ein auf dein aktuelles Fitnesslevel und deinen Rekrutierungswunsch zugeschnittenes Sportprogramm berechnen lassen. 
Ob Fallschirmaufklärer, Gebirgsspezialist, Rettungssanitäter oder Panzersappeur: Trainiere gezielt für deine Wunschfunktion in der Rekrutenschule (RS). Get ready, join #teamarmee! 

Die ready App der Schweizer Armee unterstützt dich in deiner Vorbereitung auf die Rekrutierung und Rekrutenschule. Du wirst gezielt deine Kraft, Ausdauer und mentale Stärke verbessern. Du wirst deine Fitness kontinuierlich steigern und Hintergrundinfos zu Sport, Ernährung und mentaler Stärke erhalten. Diese Vorbereitungen sind wichtig. Sie können dazu beitragen, das Verletzungsrisiko – nicht nur während der RS – zu minimieren sowie den Belastungen standzuhalten. Denn der militärische Alltag ist physisch und psychisch meist deutlich anspruchsvoller als der zivile Alltag. 

Die ready App der Schweizer Armee wurde zusammen mit dem Bundesamt für Sport BASPO nach neuesten sportwissenschaftlichen Erkenntnissen entwickelt.

- Du bekommst einen Trainingsplan, der individuell auf deine körperliche Fitness und deine angestrebte militärische Funktion abgestimmt ist.
- Pro Woche kannst du vier Trainingseinheiten mit progressiv ansteigendem Intensitätslevel absolvieren.
- Du trainierst ohne Geräte, nur mit deinem Körpergewicht.
- Für alle Übungen gibt es insgesamt über 330 Videoanleitungen.
- Die ready App kannst du auch in Kombination mit Sportuhren oder Fitnesstrackern verwenden.

descriptionHTML:
Mit der ready App der Schweizer Armee kannst du ein auf dein aktuelles Fitnesslevel und deinen Rekrutierungswunsch zugeschnittenes Sportprogramm berechnen lassen.
Ob Fallschirmaufklärer, Gebirgsspezialist, Rettungssanitäter oder Panzersappeur: Trainiere gezielt für deine Wunschfunktion in der Rekrutenschule (RS). Get ready, join #teamarmee!

Die ready App der Schweizer Armee unterstützt dich in deiner Vorbereitung auf die Rekrutierung und Rekrutenschule. Du wirst gezielt deine Kraft, Ausdauer und mentale Stärke verbessern. Du wirst deine Fitness kontinuierlich steigern und Hintergrundinfos zu Sport, Ernährung und mentaler Stärke erhalten. Diese Vorbereitungen sind wichtig. Sie können dazu beitragen, das Verletzungsrisiko – nicht nur während der RS – zu minimieren sowie den Belastungen standzuhalten. Denn der militärische Alltag ist physisch und psychisch meist deutlich anspruchsvoller als der zivile Alltag.

Die ready App der Schweizer Armee wurde zusammen mit dem Bundesamt für Sport BASPO nach neuesten sportwissenschaftlichen Erkenntnissen entwickelt.

- Du bekommst einen Trainingsplan, der individuell auf deine körperliche Fitness und deine angestrebte militärische Funktion abgestimmt ist.
- Pro Woche kannst du vier Trainingseinheiten mit progressiv ansteigendem Intensitätslevel absolvieren.
- Du trainierst ohne Geräte, nur mit deinem Körpergewicht.

title: Parkview Health
description:
Parkview is dedicated to improving health and inspiring well-being in the northeast Indiana and northwest Ohio communities we serve. The Parkview Health app connects you with a variety of helpful tools designed to enhance the patient journey.  With the app, you can start a video visit, schedule a new
patient appointment with a primary care provider, get turn-by-turn wayfinding inside the Parkview Regional Medical Center campus and more. You can even access your Parkview MyChart account from our app.

App Features

Find Your Way
   Get driving directions to a Parkview location and step-by-step wayfinding 
   around the Parkview Regional Medical Center campus.
Find a Doctor and Schedule an Appointment
   Find a new primary care provider close to you and schedule your first 
   appointment.
Find Care Now
   You now have access to more convenient care options including:
   - Emergency Care
        Find an ER location near you, view current wait times and let us know 
        you are on your way.
   - Parkview OnDemand
        24/7 access to care with a provider through from your computer, tablet 
        or smartphone.
   - eVisit
        Receive a personalized treatment plan with this symptom-based 
        questionnaire in MyChart.
   - FirstCare Walk-in Clinic
        Care for minor illnesses and injury with convenient hours and locations.
   - Parkview Ortho Express
         Specialized walk-in clinic and diagnostic imaging for orthopedic and 
         sport-related injuries.
Parkview MyChart
   You can use Parkview MyChart to:
   - View your health summary, current medications, allergies, immunizations 
        and test results.
   - Schedule and cancel appointments
   - Receive treatment from home with a virtual visit
   - Send and receive secure messages with your provider
   - Request prescription refills
   - Pay your current bill and review past payments
   - Request medical records for yourself or your proxy
                               

You must have an account to access the Parkview MyChart features. To create account, select the “Sign Up Now” button from the MyChart view in the app or visit mychart.parkview.com.

Additional app features include access to:
* Parkview Blog
* Careers
* Parkview.com

title: Inspire Sport
description:
Join millions of athletes worldwide on iNSPIRE Sport Online, to improve your mental and physical well-being and performance. Track multiple aspects of your physical and mental health, and learn how to manage your Nutrition, your Mind and your Body for optimal performance in both sport and life. 

iNSPIRE has been designed to EDUCATE, SUPPORT & iNSPIRE you on your sporting journey through intensive and interactive programs on a range of topics including Sports Psychology, Sports Science and Sports Nutrition all in the palm of your hand. With content created by industry experts and approved by athletes and coaches all over the world, you can be sure you're getting the best of the best when it comes to programs and resources. 

Track your wellness
Unlike other boring, clunky Athlete Management Systems or tracking apps, iNSPIRE has been created with the time poor athlete in mind. 

Body Health: Track your Pain and Fatigue levels to keep track of your injury, burn out and rehab programs. 

Brain Health: Stay on tack mentally by tracking your Mood and Sleep patterns to stay in control of stress and burn out. 

Food Health: Track your food choices, and meal timings to ensure you're eating enough wholesome food at regular times throughout the day. 

Performance Health: Track your training, recovery and competition sessions to stay in tune with your weekly and monthly training programs and on track physically as you chaser your goals. 

Wearable Tech
iNSPIRE has made sharing your wearable tech data super easy, via integration with Apple Health Kit / Google Fit  so all you need to do is sync your devices and your data will automatically stream into our tracking functionality. 

Educational Programs
iNSPIRE is able to bring you thousands of hours of in app content on a range of different wellness areas from Sports Psychology all the way to Performance and Recovery. 
Sports Psychology: With content created by our in house Psychologists, Annie teaches you how to manage your stress, anxiety and mood whilst learning the best tips and tricks to beat your competition through mental toughness and confidence.

Sports Nutrition: Annie takes the latest Nutrition and dietetics advice and programming from our in house Dietitians and presents it to you in a way you can genuinely understand, and gives you easy to implement tips and tricks to ensure you're fuelling your body with with absolute best range of wholesome food. 

Exercise Science: Annie works with Frankie a leading Exercise Scientist to bring you the latest recovery, injury management and performance tips from a physiological perspective. This content has been designed to help you recovery quicker & be on top of your game physically at all times. 

Stay tuned for our premium content each month where we bring in professionals and guest presenters to really ramp up the intensity. 

Through Education from our programs, combined with Support from our tracking system you are sure to feel iNSPIRED throughout your entire sporting journey, and into your professional career. Let iNSPIRE do the work for you when it comes to health programming and wellness tracking so you're able to focus on your training, performance and success.

title: Doctor Kids
description:
With the help of this game you can see what is like to be a doctor and treat kids in a children's hospital. You can make them healthy again and put a smile back on their faces. 
 
Children are coming to the clinic and they need your help to get better. Once you appoint the little patients to the right doctor’s office, you can have fun playing interactive minigames and treat kids in no time. 

Game presents different kinds of doctors and treatments, with many colorful objects to match patients’ characteristics. Every doctor’s office includes a unique minigame to make treatment even more fun. And don’t forget about the ambulance car that is always in a hurry.

Within this game, you can do the following:
Appoint your patients to the dentist to brush and fix their broken teeth. 
Diagnose patients to heal them from strange diseases.
Make an eye examination test to improve kids’ eyesight.
Use a microscope to make some lab tests and eliminate viruses. 
Use the X-ray machine to scan bones.
Drive an ambulance car and give first aid to patients.
Treat an ear infection and take a hearing test in the Xylophone minigame.

Features:
• beautiful high quality HD graphics
• intuitive, easy to use user interface
• infinite gameplay with numerous combinations
• many different patients in various clothes
• offers 7 unique doctor’s offices: dental care, eye check, skin rashes cure, lab test and X-ray, ear doctor, ambulance car with emergency room (ER doctor)
• includes 7 thematic minigames
• tons of colorful plasters, bandages, braces, glasses and syrup flavours

This game is free to play but certain in-game items and features, also some of those mentioned in game description, may require payment via in-app purchases which cost real money. Please check your device settings for more detailed options regarding in-app purchases.
The game contains advertising for Bubadu’s products or some third parties which will redirect users to our or third-party site or app.

Privacy policy: https://bubadu.com/privacy-policy.shtml
Terms of service: https://bubadu.com/tos.shtml
